Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The landscape around here has become a lot spikier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our depth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,6,750 meters, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, I can see something down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Goblet of Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine - it's just hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it is terribly humid here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The goblets of giants...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the flat-creepers are responsible for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I also hear the landscape is blue due to the mixing of\Nthe vapor they put off with the light from the force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the part that supports the flat-creepers\Nis actually a different plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The prey-trapping mechanisms of all these creepers\Nstretching out before us wither up every 2,000 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's said that then the plants below\Nall compete to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,giving rise to a completely new landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are prey-trapping mechanisms?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We actually made it here to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to how I envisioned it in my dreams,\Nit's so much damper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And my voice echoes like CRAZY!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells kinda vinegary here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find a decent place and make camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not say it out loud,\Nbut I'm sure you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That no matter how much we gloss over it,\Nthis place is right in the belly of the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The strain of ascending in the fourth layer\Nmakes you bleed out of every orifice in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If Riko's body was to undergo that, it's likely that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Commonly referred to as part of "the depths,"\Nthe probability of returning from this layer is so low
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that the third layer can't even begin to compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sprawling out here are the netherworld's goblets,\Nwhich fill up with and spill out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,various lives and aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Will those who reach out their hands\Nbe presented with fine spirits that quench their thirst,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or will they instead receive a burning poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daremo ga sakaraezu ni mogutteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono me o tomoshibi yori kagayakasete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezasu saki wa fukaku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Massugu ni mayoikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiaketa naraku no wana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu no ato o oikakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kotae ga mitsukaru nara zenbu nakushitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono koe o hanasanai youni kodama ga mada hibiiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashinban wa zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami o sashita mama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nigeba no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sore ga noroi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodou wa honmono
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nidoto akogare wa tomaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The final section of the third layer\Nhad those spiky eggs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If one hatches...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it'll become one of those squid-looking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That species still hasn't been given a name, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, less than ten percent of\Nthe creatures in the Abyss have even been named.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tens of thousands of species that-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For a little while now,\NI've been sensing a strange presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? A creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's a White Whistle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It only moves while we're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not moving right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it very likely has good hearing...\NAnd I bet it can understand our speech, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it could be also be another cave raider\Nother than just a White Whistle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even begin to pin down its position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of eerie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should get out of this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These "umbrellas" and the steam provide good cover,\Nbut walking here is difficult and visibility's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, we need to find\Nsomewhere we can camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it this one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an orbed-piercer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, don't fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that an orbed-piercer's spines\Ncan penetrate even steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're also laced with poison, and more than\None hundred cave raiders have already been kill-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sense it until it got close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a beast of the depths, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The backpack...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I dodged that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it predicted my line of retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, the Blaze Reap is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's down by its feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it actually know what that thing is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The primeval creatures of the depths that\NOzen was talking about have amazing intuition like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It should recoil from things bigger than itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, use this Scaled Umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't think that thing was nearly big enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make our way toward the Blaze Re-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the poison will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We need something to constrict it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry, Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, this is going to hurt a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, hold out your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I have to do to save Riko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blaze Reap is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's submerged...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I act as a decoy,\NRiko can't search for it in her current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My Incinerator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I faint for two hours, what will become of Riko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaping is our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, given its quickness\Nand ability to predict our movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't be able to shake it by running.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Up it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the strain of ascending in the fourth level is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,intense pain throughout the body and bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems... I don't have... much time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, pull yourself together! Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kinda strange....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, what are you talking about?\NI feel kinda strange....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, doesn't it seem like the Curse of the Abyss caused\Nthe poison to be expelled first before your own blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now to just stop the bleeding and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After... the poison's out... stop the bleed-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, I'm alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Now she's also hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that 'cause we're close to the third layer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After I wipe the blood, more streams out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I need to check on the wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's swelled to several times normal size...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-her glove... I need to take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,D-did that hurt? Sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, uh... too swollen, so I can't get the glove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to save you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt? Please just say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it... off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are you out of your mind, Riko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that, you'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if only I had made Riko stay farther behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to break the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A Black Whistle who had this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,said that cutting it off was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if only I had quickly used my Incinerator...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if only I had been a better shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I hesitate, the more Riko suffers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it goes, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what am I even doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! It's me! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too... together... to the netherworld's... bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko... your consciousness is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got an awful fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't YOU go and leave ME behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,M-my hands are shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, Riko will suffer all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not near Riko! Stay away from Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Her heart is still beating...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely to stop any moment now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a just a fluffy stuffed doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come here to comfort you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to properly introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but first wouldn't it be best to hear\Nabout how to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This's quite bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! I want to save Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to get her breathing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just blow a breath directly into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a kiss, you know, a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way, but go a little slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And pinch her nose shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, tilt up her chin to open her airway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, there's no point to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's breathing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't begin to express my gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still too early to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems she's not regaining consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she was to wake right now,\Nit's not like she'd be able to bear the pain anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You, come on and carry the girl back to my hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to do something for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you don't know anything about us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep a little distance between us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the way things stand now, her arm will break off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to reinforce it,\Nso hurry and fetch some branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can do something about her hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me warn you:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to go back to the way it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, he's not even listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I climb up this, Riko will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you can't see it then, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Curse isn't present right now, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, her whole body\Nwill swell up like her arm has.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cave-raiding equipment...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those... whistles?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey... who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I suppose I never told you my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nanachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm what you cave raiders would call...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora ni ukanderu hikaru nami o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanete niji no hashi o kakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaui ashiba, suberu slope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to mirai no michishirube
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no hidarite, boku no migite o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunaide tsunagete hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako mo ima mo mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakara mayowazu ni aruiteikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:23:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Irotoridori no yume kasanete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashita wa doko ni mukau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi to issho ni iretara, sekai wa kagayakidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Saihate no chi ni saku hana o sagasou
